data.description: This well maintained 3-bedroom house located in Lehigh Acres is fully move-in ready. A spacious office / den offers the versatility to either serve as a home office or fourth bedroom. The heart of the home is the well appointed kitchen, boasting a sizable island complemented by a serving bar that comfortably seats four. The home features an enormous fully screened rear lanai that is perfect for entertaining guests or hosting dinner parties. The immaculate backyard with lush green grass is full of various tropical fruit trees and is completely enclosed by a privacy fence to create your own secluded paradise. Completing this home's array of features are the robust hurricane shutters on every window, ensuring peace of mind and security amidst Florida's dynamic weather.
